{"tid":1089746,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"要包容？主人攬實愛犬搭巴士　網民紛嗌要投訴","createTime":"2019-04-03T04:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T04:53:00.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6db5cad9ba93f66fd0516b670ce8b1a540cb735e","tid":1089746,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"要包容？主人攬實愛犬搭巴士 網民紛嗌要投訴<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2TSWMyn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TSWMyn&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BnejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=98db6a35\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2TSWMyn</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/photo/bkn-20190403113359368-0403_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190403115449\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190403%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190403113359368-0403_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190403115449&h=216cedcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狗狗也愛搭巴士？<br />\n<br />\n寵物都可以搭巴士？近日有狗主偷運愛犬上巴士，惹來網民揶揄︰「點睇都唔係導盲犬喎」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民星期一（1日）在Facebook群組「巴士的事討論區」上傳相片，只見有中年婦抱着一隻狗狗，坐在巴士上層靠窗座位。狗狗不時伸頭四圍張望，狀甚興奮。<br />\n<br />\n發文者指該中年婦「攞個袋收埋咗（狗狗）上車」，更嘲諷謂︰「點呀？狗仔係咪覺得好逼呢&hellip;&hellip;咁就要多謝你嘅狗奴才帶你坐巴士啦，狗巴正式成立」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民建議向車長投訴︰「司機會邀請佢哋呢啲違規人士落車」、「啲人唔好咁自私啦，唔關愛唔愛狗事」、「佢又唔係導盲犬」。<br />\n<br />\n惟發文者認為當時正值繁忙時間︰「一投訴停車，結果咪搞到成車人要遲到返工&hellip;&hellip;已經即場話咗佢」，該中年婦亦向其道歉。"},{"pid":"f517082772a06cab6e161049bf6588ce569bc335","tid":1089746,"uid":136760,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:05:15.000Z","msg":"狗巴正式成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9bebf5f768a92f733fecab4f140d492ff1f301","tid":1089746,"uid":65298,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:09:43.000Z","msg":"大英祖國都俾上巴士<br />\n香港支那化嚴重先唔俾<br />\n<br />\n邊個投訴肯定係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663ae0a9f940b431099870f9507b984bd7cab311","tid":1089746,"uid":7452,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:53:00.000Z","msg":"入袋冇問題 但咁明目張膽真係認衰埋其他狗主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <span style=\"color: pink;\">班公屋狗冇車冇樓就咪學人養啦</span>"}]}